  "description": "A ***tutorial*** is a document that teaches the reader how to do something by walking them through a complete, worked example. It differs from [procedural documentation](./procedural-documentation.md) in its purpose: procedural documentation helps the reader complete a task they already understand; a tutorial teaches the reader a skill they don't yet have.",
